rem glu - Update Budget Revision
rem Program glu_budgetupdate v8.0.0 29May2006 (glu_ja)
rem Created by adx_progconv.bbx v1.0.3 (05/29/2006 12:42:53)

rem  +-----------------------------------------+
rem  | AddonSoftware Version 8.0.0 - 01Oct2006 |
